401
00:36:04,096 --> 00:36:05,629
(inhales)

402
00:36:05,631 --> 00:36:08,298
This is film
number one.

403
00:36:08,300 --> 00:36:12,702
I'm Jim Jacobs,
and we are here
at Heaven's Veil ranch.

404
00:36:12,704 --> 00:36:15,672
